24 July 2024		navdap1	TFS 65286 CUX | Include cargo structure flags in voyage API
19 Mar  2025        navsp1  JIRA-23126 CUX - API PUT /voyage responds with invalid json
10 Sept 2025		navlw1	JIRA-35882: Support External Voyage Code
*/
