23 July 2024 navhn30 ChangeRequest 65091: CUX - Add bookingId to POST /customsStatus to help uniquely identify cargo with duplicate ids
30 July 2024 navhn30 Bug 65415: CUX - Error 11051 in POST /CustomsStatus -Update not updating
09 Jun 2025 navsp1   JIRA-34865 MTN | PUT cargo endpoint doesn't correctly handle Stops with "Info Required On Clear"
*/

