        <source>tPutCargo() updating;
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
05 Apr 2024	naviv1	Initial creation TFS 63113 - CUX | PUT /cargo API - Updating cargo which has multiple prenotes - GoLCrit 01
22 Apr 2024	naviv1	TFS 63619 : CUX | FR - POST and PUT /Cargo not saving Customs References for Onboard Cargo
17 Jun 2024 navhn30 ChangeRequest 64067: CUX | Include additional fields in APIs (Free Text)
10 Jul 2024	navlw1	TFS 65030: Added prenotified":true and fixed Customer Priority as part of this bug as data difference between D/WMAST
12 Jul 2024	navlw1	TFS 64910 : CUX |  Getting Error 75766 on PUT/cargo When updating Cargo Details of Trailer
14 Aug 2024 navhn30 Bug 65220: CUX FR | CARGO - Allow updates to parent prenoted trailer in Cargo API - GoLCrit - 02
17 Sep 2024 navhn30 Bug 65980: CUX | PUT /cargo locationId should be read only
21 May 2025 navsp1  JIRA-34865 MTN | PUT cargo endpoint doesn't correctly handle Stops with "Info Required On Clear"
*/

